<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الْمُبْهَمَاتُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٩٣٧ - وَأَلَّفُوا فِي <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مُبْهَمَاتِ الْأَسْمَا»</span> … لِكَيْ تُحِيطَ النَّفْسُ مِنْهَا عِلْمَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٩٣٨ - كَـ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«رَجُلٍ»</span> وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«امْرَأَةٍ»</span> وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ابْنٍ»</span> وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«عَمّْ»</span> … <span style="color:#6c6c00">«خَالٍ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أَخٍ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«زَوْجٍ»</span> وَأَشْبَاهٍ وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أُمّْ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
